        <p>"AI-powered" has become the most overused phrase in marketing. The label is everywhere and it almost never comes with an explanation. So before you hire anyone in Miami waving that flag, it helps to know what AI genuinely changes about marketing work, what it does not change at all, and the one shift that most local agencies have not caught up to yet.</p>

